{"title":"Necklaces \u0026 Pendants","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"sagittarius-charm","title":"Sagittarius Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eDriven by the passion for knowledge, a Sagittarius explores the world fearlessly and with endless curiosity. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49186889728346,"sku":"","price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2471.jpg?v=1761346084"},{"product_id":"infinity-chain","title":"Infinity Necklace","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeavy and bold, a statement piece in solid gold 900. Every link is made by hand in my studio. This necklace is designed as a rather short choker, but any length is realisable, please \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/pages\/contact\" title=\"contact\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econtact\u003c\/a\u003e me for any personalisation. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Schuberthan Gold","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49373547692378,"sku":"","price":7000.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/Infinity-necklace-gold-on-marble.jpg?v=1769451425"},{"product_id":"aquarius-charm","title":"Aquarius Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eA creative visionary and individualist on the one hand, the Aquarius keeps his analytical mind and his sense for responsibility and reliability in every situation. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49549858373978,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2522.jpg?v=1759921536"},{"product_id":"sagittarius-charm-copy","title":"Scorpio Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eEmotional and intellectual depth make the scorpio a fascinating character, that in turn will always prefer honesty and authenticity over superficial shine.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49549944291674,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2509.jpg?v=1761346032"},{"product_id":"libra-charm","title":"Libra Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eOpen to all opinions, a libra seeks truth, justice and harmony while never forgetting about the value of beauty, fun and pleasure.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49604811981146,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2470_8565d958-71ca-4f06-a7a9-e738761dddc9.jpg?v=1760971162"},{"product_id":"capricorn-charm","title":"Capricorn Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eReliability and perseverance are core characteristics of a capricorn. Once its trust is won, it will stay loyal and never let you down. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49604958650714,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2493.jpg?v=1761346012"},{"product_id":"pisces-charm","title":"Pisces Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eWith creativity and intuition pisces follow the transformations in life effortlessly. Their natural connection to their inner feelings and their empathy for others make them a sensible character, living between reality and imagination.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49605147689306,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2516.jpg?v=1759920953"},{"product_id":"aries-charm","title":"Aries Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eAlways up for a challenge and a fresh start, aries is full of energy and enthusiasm. With its great optimism and the concentration on the positive side, for this star sign everything is reachable.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49605300781402,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2477.jpg?v=1759920787"},{"product_id":"taurus-charm","title":"Taurus Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eDown to earth but with a weakness for luxury, a taurus is reliable and solid as a rock. Living in the here and now, it makes the best out of everyday life instead of dreaming up castles in the air.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49607255753050,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2496.jpg?v=1761346056"},{"product_id":"gemini-charm","title":"Gemini Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eCurious and talkative, you will never get bored with a gemini! As they are always well informed about the latest trends and love to entertain, their energy and optimism is inspiring and contagious. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49607424573786,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2507_e75798f8-d550-4ae0-a07d-3bcbf429f2fe.jpg?v=1761303428"},{"product_id":"cancer-charm","title":"Cancer Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eA very sensitive character, cancers have great intuition and empathy and deeply care about their beloved ones. Nonetheless, they are determined and ambitious to reach their life goals.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49607561019738,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2488.jpg?v=1761307229"},{"product_id":"leo-charm","title":"Leo Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eCharismatic and generous, everyone is attracted by leo's magnetic field. As a natural leader this star sign will take care of the well being of his family and beyond and loves the recognition for these efforts.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49607566426458,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2137.jpg?v=1761345963"},{"product_id":"virgo-charm","title":"Virgo Charm","description":"\u003cp\u003eDeeply connected to the earth, a virgo takes decisions according to analytical reasoning and practical considerations. Striving for meaningfulness in life, this star sign has an authentic and strong character.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis pendant is made in 18 karat gold.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDimensions: approximately 21 x 15 x 2 mm.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"My Store","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49607569670490,"sku":null,"price":550.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC2503_6e0663b3-c735-4dd9-9f26-973f22c1914f.jpg?v=1761345921"},{"product_id":"paperclip-chain","title":"Handmade Paperclip Chain","description":"\u003cp\u003eA handmade, 18 karat gold necklace. Worn on its own it adds a \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003etouch of minimalistic elegance to any outfit. In combination with your favourite \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/collections\/pendants\"\u003ependants\u003c\/a\u003e it becomes the expression of your personal style and your story. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAs all LURI pieces, this necklace is crafted entirely by hand.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Schuberthan Gold","offers":[{"title":"45 cm","offer_id":49892760813914,"sku":"","price":1650.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":t